headline.print_headline: Thousands of Bees Attack Woman in California
headline.main: Thousands of Bees Attack Woman in California

lead_paragraph: A 71-year-old woman is believed to have suffered about 1,000 stings in Southern California after being attacked by a swarm of killer bees that covered her entire body.
